Package: httpx
Version: 1.9.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, golang
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://docs.projectdiscovery.io/tools/httpx
Description: Fast and Multi-Purpose HTTP Toolkit by ProjectDiscovery
 httpx is a lightning-fast HTTP client that allows running multiple probes
 using retryablehttp library. It is designed for security professionals
 to efficiently analyze web assets with various checks and validations.
 Features:
 - Multiple protocol support (HTTP/HTTPS)
 - Customizable probes and filters
 - Fast and reliable HTTP client
 - Title and technology detection
 - Integration with ProjectDiscovery workflow
